x402 payment facilitator on Solana. Accept crypto payments in your app with a simple TypeScript SDK. Built for developers.

Started out slinging mangos and tacos on the corner 🍉🌮 — just a hardworking frog trying to make rent and buy one cold Dos Equis 🍺. Then someone said, “Bro, ever heard of crypto?” 💻

Next thing you know, I launched $PEPELOCO on Solana — the first frog too loco for ICE 🚔 to catch. They been chasing my bags ever since, but I’m already down the block in my low rider, blasting corridos and counting gains 💵💨.

Now I don’t sell tacos… I sell dreams. 🌮➡️💰

😺 Introducing Moochi the Mochi Cat, the softest, sweetest, and most playful meme coin on Solana! 🍡✨
Moochi blends the cozy vibes of mochi with the charm of a chonky cat — creating a token that’s as adorable as it is community-driven. Built on Solana’s lightning-fast network, Moochi is here to bring fun, fluff, and wholesome energy to the meme coin scene.
